oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Maintenance Building
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Buildings; Maintenance & repair;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The campus' maintenance building was built in 1989 to be a fully functional shop with storage areas, offices, and sections for carpentry, plumbing, paint spraying, and refrigeration.
